short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Prioritize and Organize your Browser Tabs with Style

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tabpik is a tab manager that lets you organize your tabs by topics, with the purpose of continuing the use of those tabs across devices and for later use   

▬▬ FEATURES ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
- Cross Device Sync
- Prioritize content by topic and category
- Card skin change
- One click Go-to Tab 
- Search Cards/Topics
- Lock and Favor cards for frequent use

▬▬ NOTE ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
Tabpik does not save empty new tabs or chrome extension tabs
 
▬▬ KNOWN PROBLEMS ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
- Options page is still under construction
- When returning from the options page to the dashboard, the menu icon does not close on click event
